modules.description: This module computes differences between two arrays of items, producing a list of change records indicating deletions, additions, or equal segments. It operates on arrays of a user-specified item type, such as lines of text or individual characters. A concrete use case is generating line-based diffs for version-controlled documents or comparing sequences of tokens in a parser.

This module computes differences between two arrays of comparable items, generating a list of change records that indicate deletions, additions, or equal segments. It works with arrays of a user-specified item type, such as lines of text or tokens. A concrete use case is generating line-based diffs for version-controlled documents or comparing sequences of tokens in a parser.
